1
Functional cookies
These functional cookies are those the only purpose of which is to allow or facilitate communication by electronic means, or which are strictly necessary for the provision of an online communication service at the express request of the user, allowing the Site and/or our mobile game applications to function (and the user to browse/use the Site and/or our mobile applications) optimally, and to provide the user with certain online services at their request.
These cookies are not subject to user consent and are installed by default. Insofar as these cookies are necessary to offer you a better user experience or to allow you to benefit from certain functions of our Site and/or our mobile applications, we do not offer you any dedicated technical means to refuse the installation of these cookies or to disable them. Nonetheless, you do have the option of disabling them (as with certain other cookies) by other means. For example, with regard to such cookies used on our Site, you can disable them using the functions offered by you browser, while bearing in mind that in this case you risk not being able to access the Site, and/or not receiving the content and information available on the Site correctly, and/or not being able to benefit from all the Site’s functionality.
