2
Cookies for evaluation, tracking, and measurement of audience and browsing
The purpose of these cookies is to generate statistics on visits to the Site and/or our mobile game applications: tests, tracking, measurement and analysis of audience, traffic, browsing and performance.
The purpose of these cookies is to collect data regarding your use of our Site and/or our mobile game applications in order to: (i) generate statistics on visits and measure and analyze audience, traffic and browsing; (ii) evaluate, understand, and report on the way you use our Site and/or our mobile game applications (e.g. determining the way you arrive at our Site or the way you use it, determining the way you use our mobile game applications, reconstructing navigation paths); (iii) allow us to perform positioning research with regard, for example, to third-party websites or mobile applications; (iv) allow us, depending on the results obtained (depending, for example, on analysis of users’ navigation paths) to adapt our Site and/or our mobile game applications within the framework of ongoing improvement of performance and user experience.
Their functioning is based on identifying “unique visitors”, which makes it possible to measure the number of visits, the number of visitors, the number of pages viewed, the length of visit and the navigation path followed by a user, the actions and interactions of a user with our Site and/or our mobile game applications, the frequency of visits (to the Site or to specific pages on the Site or on our mobile applications), and the performance of our Site and/or our mobile applications…
