3
Cookies for the selection and distribution of personalized and/or targeted and/or geolocated content on our Site and/or our mobile game applications
The purpose of these cookies is to allow us to personalize the editorial content or the display of our products and/or services, i.e. to select and distribute, on our Site and/or on our mobile game applications, content, products and/or services for your attention based on your usage of our Site and/or our mobile game applications, your location, and also the content you have previously viewed on our Site and/or our mobile game applications, and then to evaluate their distribution and their effectiveness (i.e. audience and performance, among other things).
To this end, information regarding your usage of our Site and/or our mobile game applications is collected (e.g. information that allows us to find out where you are located, what content was displayed, how often it was displayed, how long it was displayed for, at what time and where it was displayed, and also if you reacted in response to the content, for example if you clicked on it) in order to determine by deduction your areas of interest, among other things, for the purposes of distributing to you personalized/targeted/geolocated content.
