4
Cookies for the selection and distribution of personalized and/or targeted and/or geolocated advertising on our Site and/or our mobile game applications
The purpose of these cookies is to allow us to personalize advertising, i.e. to select and distribute, on our Site and/or on our mobile game applications, content, products and/or services for your attention based on your usage of our Site and/or our mobile game applications, your location, and also the content and/or products and/or services and/or advertisements you have previously viewed on our Site and/or our mobile game applications, and then to evaluate their distribution and their effectiveness (i.e. audience and performance, among other things).
To this end, information regarding your usage of our site and/or our mobile game applications is collected (e.g. information that allows us to find out where you are located, what content and/or products and/or services and/or advertisements were displayed, how often they were displayed, how long they were displayed for, at what time and where they was displayed, and also if you reacted in response to the content and/or products and/or services and/or advertisements, for example if you clicked on them or made a purchase) in order to determine by deduction your areas of interest, among other things, for the purposes of distributing to you personalized/targeted/geolocated advertisements on our Site and/or our mobile game applications.
[to be completed with as much detail as possible]
Installation of the cookies detailed below is subject to your prior consent obtained in accordance with Article 4 hereof.
