6
Cookies for the selection and distribution of personalized and/or targeted and/or geolocated advertising on third-party websites
The purpose of these cookies is to allow us to personalize advertising, i.e. to select and distribute advertising for your attention based on your browsing, your location, and also the content and/or products and/or services and/or advertisements you have previously viewed, and then to evaluate their distribution and their effectiveness (i.e. audience and performance, among other things), and in this case in contexts other than on our Site and/or our mobile game applications, e.g. on third-party websites or applications.
To this end, information regarding your usage of our Site and/or our mobile game applications, and also of other websites and applications is collected and cross-referenced (e.g. information that allows us to find out where you are located, what content and/or products and/or services and/or advertisements were displayed, how often they were displayed, how long they were displayed for, at what time and where they were displayed, and also if you reacted in response to the content and/or products and/or services and/or advertisements, for example, if you clicked on them or made a purchase) in order to determine by deduction your areas of interest, among other things, for the purposes of selecting and distributing to you personalized/targeted/geolocated advertisements on various third-party websites or applications.
Installation of the cookies detailed below is subject to your prior consent obtained in accordance with Article 4 hereof.
